<p class="lead">Start praying. Be bold, and pray specifically.</p>

<p><em>God, thank You for sending this message to us through Isaiah. We desire to not only serve You, but to serve You with good intentions. We invite Your Holy Spirit to check our spirit as we help others, make commitments, and follow You. Amen.</em></p>

